.DT
disband_group
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
disband_group

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
disband_group -  This function does a clean removal of a group from the handler.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs void disband_group(string name,
mixed message)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the group to be disbanded
%^BOLD%^message%^RESET%^ - message to be broadcasted, if any
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/group_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function does a clean removal of a group from the handler.
If a message is specified, it is broadcasted to the group
before all members are removed.

.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
remove_group()

.EP

